# Usage Guide

{{if eq .Stack.String "go"}}## Go Project

### Prerequisites
- Go 1.22+
- golangci-lint

### Quick Start
```bash
# Build
make build

# Run tests
make test

# Lint
make lint

# Format code
make fmt
```

### Development Workflow
1. Make changes
2. Run `make fmt` to format
3. Run `make lint` to check for issues
4. Run `make test` to verify
5. Commit (pre-commit hooks will validate)

